data.description: This home is situated on a huge lot in the Lake Katherine area on a desirable street convenient to great schools & shopping. The spacious family room has a fireplace & is just off foyer. The dining room is on the opposite side of the foyer & opens to the updated kitchen that has granite counter tops, tiled back splash, painted cabinets & pantry. An updated hall bathroom with tub/shower is adjacent to the primary bedroom while two additional bedrooms share an updated jack n jill bath with tiled shower. A potential 4th bedroom is off the family room but could also be a playroom/office/media room. There's a wonderful, partially finished basement currently used as a workshop & has barn doors opening to the backyard with lots of trees & natural area for ultimate privacy. Hard to find this price point in this area!
